<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>
        <%= title %>
    </title>
    
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto+Condensed:300,400,700|Roboto:300,400,700" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.1.3/css/bootstrap.min.css' />
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/lib/css/jquery.pagepiling.min.css' />
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/css/main.css'/>
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/css/animations.css'/>
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/css/responsive.css'/>
</head>

<body>
    <header class="site-header col-12 row">
        <div class="site-logo col-2 desktop">
            <img src='/img/logo.png'>
        </div>
        <div class="nav col-12 col-sm-8">
            <ul id="menu">
                <li data-menuanchor="about" class="active"><a href="#about">About Us</a></li>
                <li data-menuanchor="services"><a href="#services">Our Services</a></li>
                <li data-menuanchor="work"><a href="#work">Our Work</a></li>
                <li data-menuanchor="contact"><a href="#contact">Contact Us</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="col-2 desktop">
            &nbsp;
        </div>
    </header>
    
    <section class="site-main col-12">
        <div id="pagepiling">

            <div class="section" id="section-about">
                <div class="logo fadeInUp-delay-500">
                    <img src="/img/logo.png">
                </div>
                <div class="introduction fadeInUp-delay-800">
                    <p class="slogan">
                        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.
                    </p>
                    <p class="content">
                        Curabitur at velit at nunc suscipit auctor. Suspendisse ut tincidunt mi. Morbi vitae egestas elit. Morbi viverra ligula nisl, ac congue risus imperdiet id. Proin venenatis lectus eu felis viverra, quis efficitur nulla placerat. Sed in commodo ipsum.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div id="intro-carousel" class="intro-carousel fadeInUp-delay-1100">
                    <button class="prev bouncingUp animation-infinite" onclick="minusSlide(1)">
                        <img src="/img/carousel-up.png">
                    </button>
                    <div class="intro-carousel-inner">
                        <div class="intro-carousel-item services active">
                            <div class="services-item">
                                <img src="/img/e-commerce.png">
                                <div class="tags">
                                    <span>Shopify</span>
                                    <span>Woo-Commerce</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="services-item">
                                <img src="/img/web-dev.png">
                                <div class="tags">
                                    <span>Landing Page</span>
                                    <span>Single Page</span>
                                    <span>Responsive</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="services-item">
                                <img src="/img/android.png">
                                <div class="tags">
                                    <span>Android</span>
                                    <span>Security</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="intro-carousel-item staff">
                            <div class="staff-item">
                                <img src="/img/e-commerce.png">
                                <div class="staff-info">
                                    <p class="name">
                                        Le Minh Son
                                    </p>
                                    <p class="position">
                                        CEO - Founder
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="staff-item">
                                <img src="/img/web-dev.png">
                                <div class="staff-info">
                                    <p class="name">
                                        Huynh Khoa Nguyen
                                    </p>
                                    <p class="position">
                                        Project Manager
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="staff-item">
                                <img src="/img/android.png">
                                <div class="staff-info">
                                    <p class="name">
                                        Shiina Mashiro
                                    </p>
                                    <p class="position">
                                        Developer
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <button class="next bouncingDown animation-infinite" onclick="plusSlide(1)">
                        <img src="/img/carousel-down.png">
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="section" id="section-services">
                <h1>Horizontal Scroll</h1>
                <p>pagePiling does it easy for you!</p>
            </div>

            <div class="section" id="section-work">
                <div class="intro">
                    <h1>Isn't it great?</h1>
                    <p>Just as you expected!</p>
                    <div id="colors2"></div>
                    <div id="colors3"></div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="section" id="section-contact">
                <div class="intro">
                    <h1>Isn't it great?</h1>
                    <p>Just as you expected!</p>
                    <div id="colors2"></div>
                    <div id="colors3"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="site-footer col-12">
        <div class="left">
            <span class="copyright">
                &copy; 2018 Devesigns. All rights reserved.
            </span>
        </div>
        <div class="right">
            <span class="email">
                <a href="javascript:void(0)">
                    contact@devesigns.com
                </a>
            </span>
            <span>
                <strong> | </strong>
            </span>
            <span class="phone">
                <a href="javascript:void(0)">
                    (+84) 123 456 789
                </a>
            </span>
        </div>
    </footer>
    <script src="/lib/js/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/lib/js/jquery.pagepiling.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>

</html>